# quantum-starter

> Modular Python starter project with professional structure, CLI, logging, and CI/CD ready.

---

## 🚀 Project Status
- **Status:** Ready for development
- **Language:** Python
- **License:** MIT

---

## 🔍 Features
- CLI tool with multiple commands
- Logging with verbose mode
- Modular folder structure
- GitHub Actions CI workflow

---

## 🛠️ Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<username>/quantum-starter.git
cd quantum-starter
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate   # macOS/Linux
.venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows
pip install -r requirements.txt  # optional
